snippet.title: A Little Late With Lilly Singh
snippet.description:
You can watch new episodes of A Little Late with Lilly Singh every Monday - Thursday at 1:35/12:35c on NBC!

Comedian, actress, social media sensation, producer and author of "How to Be a Bawse: A Guide to Conquering Life," Lilly Singh brings her unique perspective to late night as she hosts celebrity interviews, talks current events, performs musical and sketch comedy, plays games, and more. A self-proclaimed "unicorn," the multi-faceted star's debut in the late-night landscape is especially noteworthy as she's a Canadian woman of Indian descent, combining a fresh take on the day's events, pop culture, diversity and life.

A Little Late with Lilly Singh is available now on Peacock, the new streaming service from NBCUniversal.  Watch thousands of hours of hit movies and shows, plus daily news, sports, and pop culture updates.  Stream now on Peacock: https://bit.ly/3ereTp9
